headline: 2 Semiconductor Stocks with Exciting Potential and 1 to Keep Off Your Radar
summary: Semiconductors are the picks and shovels of modern technology. Compute-intensive AI workloads are also priming them for the next wave of secular growth, a trend that has supported the industry over the past six months as its 3.4% return has closely followed the S&P 500.
